---
title: Beef Koftas & DIY Yoghurt Flatbreads Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Learn how easy it is to create an airy and fluffy flatbread thanks to a surprise ingredient: yoghurt. It’s the perfect accompaniment to spiced beef koftas, a fresh tomato salad, and a spectacular mint dressing, adding just the right touch of tang.
